{"tid":939346,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【猶太戒律】猶太教徒唔食海鮮唔食豬 以色列麥記有乜食？","createTime":"2018-12-13T04:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T04:56:42.000Z","uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b956732c8d9b6d105e4d1c8d1892373a9c082011","tid":939346,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E6%88%92%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E6%95%99%E5%BE%92%E5%94%94%E9%A3%9F%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E5%94%94%E9%A3%9F%E8%B1%AC-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E9%BA%A5%E8%A8%98-064326267.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%258C%25B6%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2588%2592%25E5%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%258C%25B6%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25BE%2592%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25B1%25AC-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E8%25A8%2598-064326267.html&d=hrUMsBjfTUW8NQsFEVPQz04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=f486a5de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E6%88%92%E5%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E6%95%99%E5%BE%92%E5%94%94%E9%A3%9F%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E5%94%94%E9%A3%9F%E8%B1%AC-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E9%BA%A5%E8%A8%98-064326267.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.Bt0e9a.RFwMb6Uk0kTsEw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a9e17dc4b17ab120af1e4f16e9537d27\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.Bt0e9a.RFwMb6Uk0kTsEw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa9e17dc4b17ab120af1e4f16e9537d27&h=7ac9cc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民以食為天，想要認識「以色列」或「猶太文化」，一定要從飲食開始。<br />\n<br />\nkosher一詞於希伯來文，意謂「適合的」或「適當的」，kosher food就是符合猶太教教規的食物。因為對於嚴守戒律的猶太教徒而言，不符合kosher認可的餐廳，以及沒有kosher認可標籤的食物，統統都不能吃。而各大國際企業在以色列也作出相應對策，經營kosher食物專店，例如：麥當勞。在同一商場內會同時出現兩間麥當勞（一般及kosher麥當勞），在以色列是常態。<br />\n<br />\n猶太教派別種類多，不同派別遵守的戒條都各不相同。在此介紹三大基本猶太人食物戒律給大家稍作參考：<br />\n1) 「潔淨」與「不潔淨」<br />\n只有某些肉類、禽類與魚類是可食用。名單首先把動物分成「潔淨」與「不潔淨」兩類。「潔淨」可以吃的動物，必須能夠反芻並且腳有分趾、分蹄，例如雞、牛、羊、有鳍有鱗的魚。貝類、水生軟體動物及蝦蟹都不可食用。在以色列，大部份超市跟大賣場都買不到海鮮與豬肉。受屍體污染的水，乃是禁忌中的禁忌。<br />\n<br />\n2) 奶與肉不能並存<br />\n奶類與肉類不可混吃，所以以色列提供肉食的餐廳，通常不會同時提供加奶咖啡、有奶成份的雪糕等。<br />\n<br />\n3) 必須人道宰殺<br />\n要以「最迅速無痛，以及最人道的方法來宰殺動物」。不能吃含有動物血的食物，所以要把血放乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n基於以上種種戒律，kosher麥當勞的選擇不多，一般都以沙律為主，港人常吃的「豬柳強」及芝士漢堡，並不會在以色列有售。<br />\n<br />\n那除了麥當勞，當地有沒有快餐？耶路撒冷馬哈尼耶胡達市場（Mahane Yehuda Market）的Jahnun Bar，就是一間知名素食快餐店，有點像厚薄餅的Memulawach，更是當地人頭號最愛，每件22nis（約46港元）。客人先自行選擇新鮮配料，然後店員會為你捲好立即加熱。雖然賣相比較簡單又是全素，但豐富又新鮮的食材配上鬆脆的酵餅皮，滋味無窮。加上價格實惠又飽肚，難怪店外常出現人龍。最後，一場來到馬哈尼耶胡達市場，少不了要買手信。衫褲鞋襪香料你想得出的東西這裏都有，價錢十分貼地平民化，大家上機前記緊前來逛逛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tKmY3cG8V4sDxWOvGYGXjA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/8fabf7ad73471b01d657acabaf721adb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtKmY3cG8V4sDxWOvGYGXjA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F8fabf7ad73471b01d657acabaf721adb&h=3f178fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xQYsRoXfR.mjNqWW5G_wLQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/992be8d892dc1066820c58bed9fd5106\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxQYsRoXfR.mjNqWW5G_wLQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F992be8d892dc1066820c58bed9fd5106&h=962250b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TVlf9s5Ipvsy2DFwQezPjg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/48c166c9ac767ace87da53d5931d15d7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTVlf9s5Ipvsy2DFwQezPjg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F48c166c9ac767ace87da53d5931d15d7&h=bf71e9e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKosher meal 飛機餐食過, 超難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}